<html>
    <head>
        <title>Conectar Tumblr</title>

        <!-- Bootstrap -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-b5kHyXgcpbZJO/tY9Ul7kGkf1S0CWuKcCD38l8YkeH8z8QjE0GmW1gYU5S9FOnJ0" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        
        <!-- Favicon -->
        <link rel="icon" href="/imges/favicon.png">
        
        <!-- Font Awesome -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.3.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-mzrmE5qonljUremFsqc01SB46JvROS7bZs3IO2EmfFsd15uHvIt+Y8vEf7N7fWAU" crossorigin="anonymous">
      
        
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.js" integrity="sha256-QWo7LDvxbWT2tbbQ97B53yJnYU3WhH/C8ycbRAkjPDc=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="/dashboard/main.js"></script>
        
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/dashboard/style.css">
    </head>

    <body>
        <%- include ../../layout/menu.ejs %>
        
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-lg-12 bg-dark" id="conteudo">
                    
                    <span><h2>Conectar Tumblr</h2></span>
                    <hr>
                    <span>1- Acesse o Link: <a href="https://www.tumblr.com/oauth/apps">Register an App</a></span><br>
                    <span>2- Coloque 'http://localhost:3000' em WebSite</span><br>
                    <span>3- Coloque 'http://localhost:3000/dashboards/panel' em URL Padr√£o de CallBack</span><br>
                    <span>4- Clique em Registrar</span><br>
                    <span>5- Acesse o Link <a href="https://api.tumblr.com/console/calls/user/info">Autenticar Key</a></span><br>
                    <span>6- Insira as Key's e clique em Autenticar, e digite as 4 chaves abaixo</span><br>
                    <hr>
                    
                    <form action="/dashboards/midiasSociais/midias/conectarTumblr/conectar" method="POST">
    
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-around">
                                <input type="text" name="consumer_key" placeholder="Consumer Key" class="form-control col-md-5" required>
                                <input type="text" name="consumer_secret" placeholder="Consumer Secret" class="form-control col-md-5" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-around">
                                <input type="text" name="token" placeholder="Token" class="form-control col-md-5" required>
                                <input type="text" name="token_secret" placeholder="Token Secret" class="form-control col-md-5" required>
                            </div>

                            <input type="submit" value="Conectar" onclick='teste()' class="form-control btn btn-primary btn-block">
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>

            </div>
            
        </div>
    </body>
</html>